00:28:28,916 --> 00:28:31,626
<i>pointing out the important things in life.</i>

395
00:28:32,252 --> 00:28:33,922
<i>Values, food...</i>

396
00:28:34,588 --> 00:28:36,548
<i>the rituals that I care for.</i>

